org.jasig.cas.support.saml.services.idp.metadata.cache

Class DefaultSamlRegisteredServiceCachingMetadataResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jasig.cas.support.saml.services.idp.metadata.cache.DefaultSamlRegisteredServiceCachingMetadataResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SamlRegisteredServiceCachingMetadataResolver

    @Component(value="defaultSamlRegisteredServiceCachingMetadataResolver")
public final class DefaultSamlRegisteredServiceCachingMetadataResolver
extends java.lang.Object
implements SamlRegisteredServiceCachingMetadataResolver
    An adaptation of metadata resolver which handles the resolution of metadata resources inside a Guava cache. It basically is a fancy wrapper around Guava, and constructs the cache semantics before processing the resolution of metadata for a SAML service.
    Since:
    4.3.0
